VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)(traceback\.format_exc\(\)|traceback\.print_exc\(\)|print\(.*Exception.*\))
WHEN EXPR MISSING:(DEBUG=False|logger\.exception|logging\.exception|production)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects code that exposes stack traces or sensitive error information in Python applications.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Stack Trace or Error Disclosure.
